node.text:
who gave their time to be on No Filter with Naomi .  Celebrating our 1 st Anniversary !!Started this by putting my IPAD on a pile of books on my dinning table , dressed sometimes from waist up !! .. I hope this has  bought some polite distraction hearing our conversations  in these challenging times , to  @kindredmediahq  @aryehbourkoff and @sidrasmithofficial @essence for stepping in to sponsor and keeping the wheels turning .. and to my incredible team who have been there since day 1 @derekblasberg, @stevengrossman , Alex Kovacs, @chamberschris, Blythe , Peter and Sam at shortcuts @Terripitts @akeemjr... #Sasha @shortcutsediting 
Thank you , love  to you all ❤️❤️❤️❤️ @cindycrawford @diddy @carlabruniofficial @cturlington @nicolerichie @themarcjacobs @ashleygraham @pppiccioli @leedaniels @adutakech @sharonstone @parishilton @venuswilliams @serenawilliams @karliekloss @jackieaina @opalayo @real_sharpton @alphonsodavid @bethannhardison @tylersphotos @cynthiaerivo @chrisrock @katehudson @gabunion @therealmaryjblige @jamescharles @whoopigoldberg @chelseahandler @camerondiaz @femiakuti @iamishasesay @lizakoshy @thepatriciabright @lilly @mariahcarey @drseemayasmin @wizkidayo @majimb.o @goldarosheuvel @andradaymusic @rayformayor @traceeellisross @bravoandy @pharrell @jpgaultierofficial @sholamos1 @parisjackson @davechappelle 🙏🏾❤️

node.title: To My Panthers , So grateful  to all these  amazing Guests

node.text: MANDELA DAY!! HAPPY BIRTHDAY TATA #NELSONMANDELA . MY UNCONDITIONAL HERO!! SO GRATEFUL AND BLESSED TO BE IN YOUR LIFE LAST 20 YEARS…YOU WERE ALWAYS SO HUMBLE, SHARING YOUR WISDOM. ENCOURAGING ALL TO REACH THEIR GOALS, THE SILENCE THAT WE WOULD SIT IN SPEAKS VOLUMES TO ME NOW, EVEN MORE SO NOW , THAN THEN. YOU ARE A TESTAMENT OF POSITIVE ACTION. WE WILL NOT LET THAT BE IN VAIN!!! I LOVE YOU ALWAYS &FOREVER  #AMANDLA #NAOMIAFRICA ❤️🎂🇿🇦❤️🤍🇿🇦❤️🎂❤️#mandeladay

node.text:
Congratulations 🇮🇹 
  The minute the game was over my mind said I hope the England team will be ok mentally,  I know pressure but , nothing like what both teams must  have felt  today , with intention to bring glory to their respected countries .. It’s with heavy heart I have to hear and read such disgusting racial comments , easy to be a hater , BUT it’s not easy what you  players do ! .. I can Only tell you I’ve lived this on a smaller scale ,  and I want to let you know HOW PROUD I AM OF YOU ALL , AS YOU GAVE YOUR ALL ,  AND DONT LET THE IGNORANT VOICES IN .. STAY ON YOUR LEVEL , DREAM BIGGER, REACH HIGHER AND LET THAT DRIVE YOU .. AS YOU ARE WINNERS FULFILLING YOUR LIFE LONG PASSION ⚽️❤️⚽️❤️ 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿🙏🏾 #STOPTHEHATE #STOPRACISM
